Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:40:43 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] rapier - 1.8 combat: disable mace smash attack and fall
 damage negation

canSmashAttack always returns false, which disables the damage bonus,
particle effects, fall distance reset, and knockback radius effect.
mace becomes a regular weapon (still has base attack damage).

diff --git a/net/minecraft/world/item/MaceItem.java b/net/minecraft/world/item/MaceItem.java
index c9e6cf2643333a49cda78bbe2956b0f8a9b8a996..1945f42c2814a04af3c9f78f8f9f1384f8b1daa9 100644
--- a/net/minecraft/world/item/MaceItem.java
+++ b/net/minecraft/world/item/MaceItem.java
@@ -166,6 +166,7 @@ public class MaceItem extends Item {
     }
 
     public static boolean canSmashAttack(LivingEntity entity) {
+        if (true) return false; // rapier - 1.8 combat: disable mace smash attack and fall damage negation
         return entity.fallDistance > 1.5 && !entity.isFallFlying();
     }
 
